ruleLogicalInfo.ruleDesc: Verify ICD Version code value for In Patient Facilty claims with Discharge date >10/1 (claim service start date could be <10/1), the claims should be ICD 10 compliant  i.e  ICD_VERSION_CD should be populated as 10.

paramsVOLst.paramValue:
SEL *  FROM  #PRM_EDW_DATABASE#.CLM_LINE
WHERE CLM_ADJSTMNT_KEY IN (
SEL  CLM_ADJSTMNT_KEY FROM  #PRM_EDW_DATABASE_2#.FCLTY_CLM
WHERE  ICD_VRSN_CD <> '10'
AND DSCHRG_DT>  ('2015-09-30')
AND CLM_SOR_CD IN #PRM_CLM_SOR_CD# )
AND CLM_SOR_CD IN #PRM_CLM_SOR_CD#
AND ( ADJDCTN_DT>  ('2015-09-30') AND CLM_LINE_STTS_CD<>'DND' AND  CLM_LINE_SRVC_STRT_DT >  ('2015-09-30'))
AND ((#PRM_INCR_FLAG# = '2'
AND ( UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW# OR LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW#)) 
OR(#PRM_INCR_FLAG# <> '2'AND ( UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW# 
OR CRCTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_CRCTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW# OR LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW#)) 
OR (#PRM_DATAPROF_FLAG# = '2'))
